。自分の意見を補強(support)する証拠（evidence: numbers or names）をリサーチし、具体的に示しながら意見を述べてください。</div></div><div>4．1.～3．をひとつのワードファイルにしてLUNAの「課題」に提出（アップロード）してください）。</div><div>締切：コアウィークス⑨の授業日の23：59</div>", ""], "第8回": ["<span lang=\"EN-US\" 游明朝\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"游明朝',serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:'times\" new=\"new\" roman\";mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"roman';mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">【コアウィークス⑥】</span><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">対面授業</span><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">／</span><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">《90分》</span></span><div><span lang=\"EN-US\" 游明朝\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"游明朝',serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:'times\" new=\"new\" roman\";mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"roman';mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">Presentation skills: Physical message and Visual message、グループ分け</span></div>", ""], "第9回": ["<span lang=\"EN-US\" 游明朝\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"游明朝',serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font